episodes.title: S7,E18: Annie Dawid - Staying persistent when getting rejected
episodes.description: It can get really frustrating & discouraging sometimes when you submit your book to a publishing company and they reject your manuscript. Listen in as Annie talks with us about how she refused to give up & she stayed persistent! To get copies of the book: Amazon & most booksellers --- Support this podcast: https://podcasters.spotify.com/pod/show/yourwritingtable/support
